```plantuml
@startuml serverdevcamp_camp4_quadcore
actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "Auth Front" as AuthFront
participant "Auth Server" as AuthServer
participant "Data Pipeline" as DataPipeline
participant "Data Processing" as DataProcessing
participant "Data Sending" as DataSending
participant "User Activity" as UserActivity
database "Cassandra DB" as Cassandra
database "Redis" as Redis
database "Kafka" as Kafka

User -> Frontend: Access Dashboard
Frontend -> APIGateway: Request Data
APIGateway -> AuthServer: Validate JWT
AuthServer -> Redis: Check Refresh Token
AuthServer -> APIGateway: JWT Validated
APIGateway -> DataPipeline: Fetch Twitter Data
DataPipeline -> Kafka: Ingest Data
Kafka -> DataProcessing: Process Data with Spark
DataProcessing -> Cassandra: Store Processed Data
DataProcessing -> DataSending: Send Real-Time Data
DataSending -> UserActivity: Update User Feeds
UserActivity -> Cassandra: Fetch User Data
DataSending -> Frontend: Push Real-Time Updates
Frontend -> User: Display Data

@enduml
```